            . I am an <rs id="t18200112-100-viclabel557" type="occupation">upholder</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-100-victim1006 t18200112-100-viclabel557"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18200112-100-crimeloc558">Tottenham-court-road</placeName>
